        <sponsor name-id="S311">Ms. Klobuchar</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="S287">Mr. Cornyn</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S282">Mr. Nelson</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S337">Mr. Coons</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name added-display-style="italic" committee-id="SSJU00" deleted-display-style="strikethrough">Committee on the Judiciary</committee-name>
